Your style reflects in everything you do. To stand out, you must therefore be creative in your own way. Interestingly, the off Shoulder outfit design is one option you cannot ignore for those formal events and they would surely make you stand out. To do justice to your outlook, you can add some simple or classic accessories to jazz it up in style. Glamourous shoes, handbags, earrings, bangles would definitely help to dress it up or down! And you will be glad that you did. Tips